{
  "stem": "16503.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she-- we knew that we cannot keep it up with our no strengths and her not being able to stand.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, we got caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was-- we were ordered to take her to the infirmary-- whatever, I mean, this is a fancy word.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't even that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My sister was too weak, so I kind of dragged her down the path into the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took her, and it was awful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The place was smelly, as I said so many times, and I'm repeating myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that infirmary-- oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was just awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were sick people there, dead people there, and on top of each other, propped against the wall.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it, it was just hideous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother turned to me, and of course, we spoke Czech, and I will not speak Czech, but I will translate it to you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said to me-- my name is Vera, but she used to use the endearment of my name-- [CZECH], how can you leave me in a place like this?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if your heart isn't torn out of you at that point, it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did not have a choice at all-- none.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to leave her there, and that is the last time I saw my mother alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I live with those words ringing in my ears.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know, I know so well that I couldn't have done anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm living with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Believe me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We inquired [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about her, and we were not allowed there, and we never heard anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was pretty much the story of my mother's life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a wonderful mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
